**/*IntegrationTests/
**/*Tests/
**/TestResults/
**/coverage/
**/test/
**/tests/

# Development Tools
tools/

# Documentation
*.md
docs/

# Configuration (not needed in container)
**/appsettings.Development.json
**/appsettings.Local.json
.editorconfig
LICENSE
global.json
renovate.json
stylecop.json

# NuGet
**/*.nupkg
**/nuget.config
**/packages/

# Temporary & Log Files
*.cache
*.log
*.temp
*.tmp

# OS Files
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# Secrets & Certificates (should never be in container)
*.pfx
*.pem
*.key
**/secrets/

# Docker (prevent recursive context)
**/.env
**/Dockerfile*
docker-compose*.yml
